<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<aiml>

<category>
  <pattern>HELLO</pattern>
  <template>
    Hi 👋 I am your Conversational Design Tutor.

    You can:
    - START COURSE
    - SHOW TOPICS
    - QUIZ ME
    - PRACTICE MODE
  </template>
</category>

<category>
  <pattern>START COURSE</pattern>
  <template>
    <think><set name="lesson">1</set></think>
    Great. Starting your learning journey.

    Say NEXT LESSON to continue.
  </template>
</category>

<category>
  <pattern>NEXT LESSON</pattern>
  <template>
    <condition name="lesson">
      <li value="1">
        Lesson 1: Conversational Design Basics.
        It is about designing helpful, human-like conversations.
        <think><set name="lesson">2</set></think>
      </li>
      <li value="2">
        Lesson 2: User Intent.
        Understanding what the user wants is key.
        <think><set name="lesson">3</set></think>
      </li>
      <li value="3">
        Lesson 3: Bot Persona.
        Defines tone and personality of the chatbot.
        <think><set name="lesson">4</set></think>
      </li>
      <li value="4">
        Lesson 4: Conversation Flows.
        Structure of interaction between user and bot.
        <think><set name="lesson">5</set></think>
      </li>
      <li value="5">
        Lesson 5: Error Handling.
        Good bots recover from confusion.
      </li>
    </condition>
  </template>
</category>

<category>
  <pattern>SHOW TOPICS</pattern>
  <template>
    Topics:
    - Basics
    - Intent
    - Persona
    - Flows
    - Error Handling

    Say LESSON PERSONA or TEACH ME FLOWS.
  </template>
</category>

</aiml>